---
const stack = ['TypeScript', 'Go', 'Kubernetes', 'Terraform', 'PostgreSQL', 'Cloudflare', 'AWS', 'Azure'];
---

<section id="home" class="section-y">
  <div class="container-zen">
    <div class="grid items-end gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-10">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <p class="animate-fade-up eyebrow opacity-0 [animation-delay:0ms]">ZenKube · consulting &amp; build</p>
        <h1
          class="animate-fade-up mt-5 font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.06] tracking-tight text-white opacity-0 sm:text-5xl lg:text-[2.65rem] xl:text-6xl [animation-delay:60ms]"
        >
          Calm delivery for
          <span class="gradient-text"> serious systems.</span>
        </h1>
        <p
          class="animate-fade-up mt-6 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400 opacity-0 [animation-delay:120ms] sm:text-lg"
        >
          We help you tighten architecture, ship reliable software, and run platforms you can explain to finance—not slide
          decks that age in a week.
        </p>
        <div
          class="animate-fade-up mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 opacity-0 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:items-center [animation-delay:180ms]"
        >
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary w-full min-w-[11rem] sm:w-auto">Start a conversation</a>
          <a href="#services" class="btn-ghost w-full min-w-[11rem] sm:w-auto">See how we work</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <aside
        class="animate-fade-up surface-muted relative overflow-hidden p-8 opacity-0 lg:col-span-5 [animation-delay:140ms]"
      >
        <div
          class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-12 top-0 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/15 blur-3xl"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>
        <p class="eyebrow text-emerald-200/70">Engagement shape</p>
        <p class="mt-4 font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white">Short discovery, then build.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">
          We prefer thin slices of working software over months of abstract planning. You keep ownership; we bring pace
          and rigor.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 border-t border-white/10 pt-6 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <li class="flex justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/[0.05] pb-3">
            <span>Typical first deliverable</span>
            <span class="shrink-0 font-medium text-zinc-300">2–4 weeks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between gap-4">
            <span>How we collaborate</span>
            <span class="shrink-0 font-medium text-zinc-300">Async + weekly sync</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <div
      class="animate-fade-up mt-14 flex flex-col gap-4 border-t border-white/[0.07] pt-10 opacity-0 [animation-delay:220ms] sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"
    >
      <p class="eyebrow text-zinc-500">Stacks we ship in often</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 sm:justify-end" aria-label="Technologies">
        {
          stack.map((name) => (
            <span class="rounded-md border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-400">
              {name}
            </span>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="surface-muted animate-fade-up p-6 opacity-0 [animation-delay:260ms]">
        <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white">Evidence-led</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">Metrics, logs, and cost before opinions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="surface-muted animate-fade-up p-6 opacity-0 [animation-delay:300ms]">
        <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white">Small teams</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">No bait-and-switch to a bench you never meet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="surface-muted animate-fade-up p-6 opacity-0 [animation-delay:340ms]">
        <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white">Plain language</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">Architecture notes your leads can actually read.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
